Join Azure VM to Domain

Description:

Join the Azure VM <VM_NAME> in resource group <RESOURCE_GROUP> to the example.local Active Directory domain using service account domainjoinuser. Ensure network connectivity to domain controllers and proper DNS configuration.

Acceptance Criteria:

VM is joined to the domain.

VM appears in AD Computers.

Domain users can log in.

DNS resolves the domain correctly.

Steps are documented in the ticket.
